        <body>


            <div type="edition">
               <div type="textpart" xml:id="SelectionMary">
                  <label>On how St. Mary was selected.</label>
                  <ab>ከመ፡ ተኃርየት፡ ድንግል፡ ማርያም፡ ለከዊነ፡ እመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡</ab>
               </div>

               <div type="textpart" xml:id="MaryLineageDavid">
                  <label>One tells that she was from the lineage of David.</label>
                  <ab>ዘይዜኑ፡ ከመ፡ ኮነት፡ እም፡ ነገደ፡ ዳዊት፡</ab>
               </div>

                  <div type="textpart" xml:id="MaryJoseph">
                     <label>One explains that this virgin was engaged with Joseph.
                     </label>
                     <ab>ዘያሌቡ፡ ከመ፡ ዛቲ፡ ድንግል፡ ተፍህተት፡ ለዮሴፍ፡</ab>
                  </div>

                  <div type="textpart" xml:id="MaryPoor">
                     <label>One tells that the Mother of God was poor<gap reason="lost"/>.</label>
                     <ab>ዘይዜኑ፡ ከመ፡ ወላዲተ፡ አምላክ፡ ኮነት፡ ነዳይት፡ ውስተ፡<gap reason="lost"/>
               </ab>
                  </div>


               <div type="textpart" xml:id="Annonciation">
                  <label>One tells how Angel Gabriel was sent to her.</label>
                  <ab>ዘይዜኑ፡ ከመ፡ ተፈነወ፡ ኀቤሃ፡ ገብርኤል፡ መልአከ፡ ለአብስሮ፡</ab>
               </div>

               <div type="textpart" xml:id="DecreeAugustusCaesar">
                  <label>One tells as to how this was orderedOctavianus Caesar Augustus.</label>
                  <ab>ዘይነግር፡ ትእዛዘ፡ ዝኩ፡ አክጥትያኖስ፡ አውግስጦስ፡ ቄሳር።</ab>
               </div>

               <div type="textpart" xml:id="ChristBetlhehemJerusalem">
                  <label>One tells that Christ chose Bethlehem to be born there,
                    and Jerusalem to die there.</label>
                    <ab>ዘይዜኑ፡ ከመ፡ ክርስቶስሃ፡ ኃረየሃ፡ ለቤተ፡ ልሔም፡ ይትወለድ፡
                      ባቲ፡ ወይሙት፡ በኢየሩሳሌም።</ab>
               </div>

               <div type="textpart" xml:id="PeacefulTime">
                  <label>About the peaceful time when the heavenly palace descended
                  upon us from above.</label>
                  <ab>ዘይዜኑ፡ ዘመነ፡ ሰላማዊት፡ ዘባቲ፡ መጽአ፡ ኀቤነ፡ እምላዕሉ፡
                  ዝኩ፡ ታዕካ፡ ሰላማዊት፡</ab>
               </div>


               <div type="textpart" xml:id="Signs">
                  <label>One tells that there were many signs and great prophecies before
                  the advent of Christ, and why they took place.</label>
                  <ab>ዘይዜኑ፡ ከመ፡ ኮኑ፡ ብዙኃን፡ ትእምርታት፡ ወባሕላት፡ ዓቢያት፡ እምቅመ፡ መጽአቱ፡
                  ለክርስቶስ፡ ወከመ፡ በእንተ፡ ምክንያት፡ ኮኑ፨</ab>
                  </div>


